		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.huacao77.com/?p=11882</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[柑橘类水果是人们喜欢吃的水果之一，尤其是最近两年大火的砂糖橘，每家人过年必备上几箱子的水果。 柑橘类水果甜，汁 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">柑橘类水果是人们喜欢吃的水果之一，尤其是最近两年大火的砂糖橘，每家人过年必备上几箱子的水果。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/6646acd8da178086f97cd8a2eec3bca4.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">柑橘类水果甜，汁水丰富，成为人们喜欢吃的水果之一。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/d493895afed63bc2edfb9f41dc6d6529.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">柑橘类水果包括柑、橘、橙，柚子。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">一、砂糖橘</span></strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/850a6a511030d4aa511542123f97e4d1.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ce3c617180897110e39823771ec9e88b.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">是这几年过年必备的标志水果，吃起来甜，水分充足。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">果实扁圆形，颜色橙黄或橙红，果肉肥厚，果壁薄，易剥离，鲜美极甜，无渣，口感细腻，果香浓郁。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">二、丑橘</span></strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/f32f93af824cc84b8e60ea50c403f3dc.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/179a144e4a94ed0d5a2a618a6584fd90.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">从日本引进的品种，果实为倒卵形，皮黄橙色，果皮皱，皮厚，易剥离，口感清脆，水分充足，酸甜可口。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">三、金桔</span></strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/4c2181f1d1b9d18942afede3c6cdc936.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/6c93690ed31e82268e6a4c9524a6c664.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">又称金枣，脆皮桔，果实近圆形，果小，果皮薄且脆，色泽鲜红，易剥离，可以连皮吃，味道味甜，芳香味浓郁。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">四、耙耙柑</span></strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/611e58f42a744b331b3705cbb8865316.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/a1af4e817fed61bb518d58ebfaa454e3.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">果实高扁圆形，果形大，甜度高，风味浓郁，果皮较软，有光泽，果肉和果皮之间基本不粘连，肉质细嫩，水分大。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">五、脐橙</span></strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/f39feeef817fd4a10ca312720b04bb75.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/f44b014c59ac1261423631ac00b06342.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">果面橙红色，光滑，肉质脆嫩，籽小汁多，酸甜适度。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">六、沃柑</span></strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/1d67b18b1e94f0996d90471779b0cfb0.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">果个大，皮薄，好剥离，清香浓郁，甜度高，耐储存。同时有橙和橘的优点。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">七、血橙</span></strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/dc1cff78b4af200cebfd2d4420e1574d.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/c7378b9662550afa68d58641a03f3b0c.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">脆嫩多汁，酸甜可口，果皮橙红色，较难剥离，汁水丰富，果肉为红色。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">八、皇帝柑</span></strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/706f60b1fca846a7a2d09cc7eeb775e7.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">皮薄多汁，青黄皮风味好，水分多，好剥离，清甜。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">九、芦柑</span></strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/194a40e20d40bb20a9a3b80654b4983f.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">果实大，颜色鲜艳，皮松易剥离，肉质脆嫩，汁水多，芳香味浓。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;"><span style="color: green;">十、甜橙</span></strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/1992b8e1ee489fb88d305c72a759fdd2.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/5b3f1fc8c1466a1c4a1c2bc51af38819.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">糖分高，甜度高，汁水丰富。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">柑橘类水果虽然好吃，但不要一次性多吃哦。</p>


</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
